{"tid":2487621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警察投訴課正式回覆許智峯所有投訴均不成立，該警員「並無過錯」，監警會亦同意該結論。","createTime":"2021-04-13T16:11:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:28:59.000Z","uid":156652,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0166cee36bca871a6abd6167cdc300b3a558622b","tid":2487621,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"2020年1月1日元旦遊行，許智峯在黃金廣場外與警員理論時被兩次脫去眼罩及被近距離噴胡椒。事隔一年零三個月，警察投訴課正式回覆許智峯所有投訴均不成立，該警員「並無過錯」，監警會亦同意該結論。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯在FB回應：「暴政當道，無人會對淪落的警隊有任何期望，只要政治正確，政權會包庇警員任何卑劣行徑。公開此信，是要將警暴公諸於世，將暴政的惡行寫在歷史，讓香港警察永遠被人民唾棄。我們絕不要習慣荒繆與黑暗，香港人加油。」<br />\n<br />\nOn 2020.1.1, a police officer took off Ted Hui's goggles twice &amp; pepper sprayed him &amp; journalists at Causeway Bay. 1 year later, CAPO replied that all of Ted's complaints were unsubstantiated. The officer was not at fault. IPCC agreed with the conclusion.<br />\n<br />\nVideo by Studio Incendo (CC BY 4.0)"},{"pid":"05d3c3eedc8d67f241601aee93a855b0300f7bbe","tid":2487621,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6135f741370c4c63ea53a15a5c2db3924529c1","tid":2487621,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:57:31.000Z","msg":"連片推上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebf358415c3a3eb575927c57823f4e83953dfdd","tid":2487621,"uid":266131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:57:47.000Z","msg":"所有制度內既反抗都係哂氣"},{"pid":"9a9dbc716c0b257864083046002f2eab453a42e2","tid":2487621,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a617ccc5eb7409a4ddaba0417a0814b036fa88","tid":2487621,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"<i